### Redis Bitfield Operations (Simulated)
### Set a bitfield value
POST {{BaseUrl}}/bitfield/user:permissions/set
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offset": 0,
  "width": 8,
  "value": 255
}

### Get a bitfield value
POST {{BaseUrl}}/bitfield/user:permissions/get
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offset": 0,
  "width": 8
}

### Increment a bitfield value
POST {{BaseUrl}}/bitfield/counters/incrby
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "offset": 0,
  "width": 32,
  "increment": 1
}

### Set multiple bitfield values using multi-operation
POST {{BaseUrl}}/bitfield/game:stats/operations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operations": [
    {
      "operation": "SET",
      "offset": 0,
      "width": 16,
      "value": 1000
    },
    {
      "operation": "SET", 
      "offset": 16,
      "width": 16,
      "value": 500
    },
    {
      "operation": "SET",
      "offset": 32,
      "width": 16,
      "value": 250
    }
  ]
}

### Get bitfield information
GET {{BaseUrl}}/bitfield/game:stats/info

